snippet.textDisplay:
New Hallmark Movie: Ginger Wed

Ginger is the daughter of a baker, but he passed away when she was very young. The one thing she remembers from him is the delicious taste of his gingerbread cookies. She became a world renown cookie taster, to try and get the taste of her Father's cookies again. After fifteen years, she (25) moves back into her old home town, unable to get that taste. She meets a new man who had moved near her childhood home, and he's a baker. Will this new man reawaken her taste for the holidays?

New Hallmark Movie: Ginger Wed

Ginger is the daughter of a baker, but he passed away when she was very young. The one thing she remembers from him is the delicious taste of his gingerbread cookies. She became a world renown cookie taster, to try and get the taste of her Father's cookies again. After fifteen years, she (25) moves back into her old home town, unable to get that taste. She meets a new man who had moved near her childhood home, and he's a baker. Will this new man reawaken her taste for the holidays?
